:Class region

    :field public id
    :field public shape 
    :field public periodic
    :field public pos
    :field public subregions

    ∇ Compose args
      :Access public
      :Implements constructor
      :If 'box'≡⊃args
          (shape pos)←1↓args
      :EndIf
      ⍝ Default non-periodic
      periodic←0
    ∇
:EndClass
